room_title: Escape room "Wild West Saloon" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
review: This place is really awesome! James was super cool, kind, and fun! I highly recommend this place for a fun evening with friends or family! Can't wait to try their other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Wild West Saloon" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
review: First time at an escape room and I have to say this was an awesome experience. The assistant there was great and helpful. The place is clean and organized. Can't wait to go back.

room_title: Escape room "Wild West Saloon" by Challenge Escape Rooms in New York
review: Fun experience! There were 10 of us and we all had a fun time. We did the new saloon room, and we didn't escape. Would recommend.
